```
![Screenshot of the embed example](img/svgEmbed1.png)

## Animation Example

```
utils.svg.embed(({ el, SVG, width, height }) => {
    var rect1 = el.rect(100, 100)
        .move(width/2, 0);

    rect1.animate(1000, 0, 'absolute')
        .move(width/2, 100)
        .loop(true, true);
})
```
